genki.text:
Applies a sliding effect to an image.
 Options:
 interval - empty space between frames in pixels.
 speed - sliding speed.

pat.text:
Headpats an image.
 Options:
 squish (0 to 100)
 offsetx (positive or negative value)
 offsety (positive or negative value)
 relative main (applies offset to image instead of hand)

roll.text:
Applies a rolling effect.
 Options:
 rotationspeed
 speed

rotate.text:
Applies a rotating effect.
 Options:
 rotationspeed

santa.text: Places a santa hat over the image. Uses same options as pat.

shake.text:
Applies a shaking effect.
 Options:
 delay ( 1 to 100) - delay between frames in centisecs. 
 intensity (1 to 124) - shaking intensity

speed.text:
Speeds up a gif.
 Options:
 delay ( 1 to 100) - delay between frames in centisecs.

spiral.text:
Applies a spiral effect to an image.
 Options:
 rotationspeed
 zoom

zoom.text:
Applies a zooming effect to an image.
 Options:
 zoom - zooming power/speed
